text: 173 is a number. It comes after 172 and before 174. == In Mathematics == *173 is a prime number, which means it can only be divided by 1 and itself. *It is part of a group called Chen primes, a special type of prime numbers. *173 is the sum of three consecutive prime numbers: 53, 59, and 61.
